page.title: 19SKIPPING RHYMES
page.content: {1)}Not last night but the night before 24 robbers came knocking at the door, As I went out they came in and knocked me on the head with a rolling pin, Ballerina,Ballerina turn around, Ballerina,Ballerina touch the ground, Ballerina,Ballerina do the kicks Ballerina,Ballerina show your Knicks Yes/no/yes/no{ {====================================== {2)}Bumble bee bumble bee chase me round the apple tree.Bumble bee bumble bee chase me into the sea. {====================================== {3)}Theres someone under the bed I don't know who it is I feel very frightened so Cathy must come in, Cathy lit the candle,Cathy lit the gas Go out Rachael,Go out Rachael, YOU SILLY LITTLE ASS.
